Metasploit Framework

The world’s most used penetration testing framework

Knowledge is power, especially when it’s shared. A collaboration
between the open source community and Rapid7, Metasploit helps
security teams do more than just verify vulnerabilities, manage
security assessments, and improve security awareness; 

it empowers and arms defenders to always stay one step (or two)
ahead of the game. 

This is a repackage of the official nightly build of the debian
package by Rapid7

Security note: the bundled payload and exploit binaries are shipped
executable, as Metasploit requires. They are delivery artifacts used
against remote targets, not programs meant to be run on the host.
